channel.description:
[IMG]http://imageshack.us/a/img809/4290/jamscapelogo.png[/img]
[URL=http://"http://jam-scape.com"]Website[/URL] [URL=http://"http://jam-scape.com/forums/forum.php"]Forums[/URL] [URL=http://"http://jam-scape.com/jamscape.jar"]Download Client[/URL] [URL=http://"http://jam-scape.com/highscores/"]Highscores[/URL] [URL=http://"http://jam-scape.com/vote/"]Vote[/URL]
[B]An Introduction[/B] Jam-Scape is a really great server, from being #18th on google and a 317 RSPS it has grown substantially into a 718 server what is slowly growing to be a really rather great server. From home at Ooglog to fighting top/custom monsters in the game, Jam-Scape has it all... we are also 24/7 uptime and a new, clean and sleek website what is very user friendly... come and sign up at the forums for new updates and sneek previews of future updates! see you ingame!
[B]Miscellaneous Features[/B] Advanced teleportation tab WIP Achievement Tab Fight Caves and Kiln Dominion Tower Barrows Duel Arena Castle Wars Fight Pits Godwars Bosses (Incl. Nex) Corporeal Beast King and Queen Black Dragon Kalphite Queen Tormented Demons Hati Wolf Wolverine (Custom NPC) Jake (Custom NPC) Easter Minigame Avatar of Destruction Nomad Glacors Polypore Dungeon Slayer Tower Kuradel's Slayer Dungeon Mutated Jadinko Lair Forinthry Dungeon
[B]Skilling Features[/B] All 25 Skills trainable Farming with growing Dungeoneering to 120 Hunter - Puro Puro and Bird/Chinchompa Trapping Summoning - Pouch creation Construction - Create Furniture Slayer - Tasks skipping and rewards Mining - Lava flow mining and LRC Smithing - Armour/Weapon forging and Artisan's Workshop Agility - Gnome and Barbarian Courses (Incl. Advanced) Herblore - Extreme/Overload making Thieving - Stall thieving Crafting - Gem cutting Fletching - Making bows Runecrafting - Crafting runes Prayer - Bones on altar Magic - All spellbooks Ranged - Ava's and Chaotic Crossbow Dungeoneering - Unique dungeon kill for exp and tokens
